{"id":85,"count":2,"description":"<strong data-start=\"0\" data-end=\"28\">Magical Himachal Special<\/strong> \u2013 A perfect escape to the enchanting hills of Himachal Pradesh, where snow-clad mountains, pine forests, and charming valleys await you. From the lively streets of Shimla and the romantic aura of Manali to the serene beauty of Dharamshala and Dalhousie, Himachal offers a magical blend of adventure, spirituality, and natural charm. Whether it\u2019s enjoying snowfall, exploring ancient temples and monasteries, or indulging in thrilling activities like paragliding and river rafting, this trip makes every moment unforgettable in the lap of the Himalayas.","link":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/destinations\/himachal-pradesh\/","name":"MAGICAL HIMACHAL SPECIAL","slug":"himachal-pradesh","taxonomy":"destination","parent":0,"meta":[],"thumbnail":{"width":1200,"height":675,"file":"2025\/09\/Himachal-pradesh.webp","filesize":155526,"sizes":{"medium":{"file":"Himachal-pradesh-300x169.webp","width":300,"height":169,"filesize":18150,"mime_type":"image\/webp","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Himachal-pradesh-300x169.webp"},"large":{"file":"Himachal-pradesh-1024x576.webp","width":1024,"height":576,"filesize":142206,"mime_type":"image\/webp","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Himachal-pradesh-1024x576.webp"},"thumbnail":{"file":"Himachal-pradesh-150x150.webp","width":150,"height":150,"filesize":9268,"mime_type":"image\/webp","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Himachal-pradesh-150x150.webp"},"medium_large":{"file":"Himachal-pradesh-768x432.webp","width":768,"height":432,"filesize":95136,"mime_type":"image\/webp","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/Himachal-pradesh-768x432.webp"},"trip-thumb-size":{"file":"Himachal-pradesh-374x226.webp","width":374,"height":226,"filesize":